@atif-rehman-ideofuzion Well, it seems to be working fine for me with RTX2070 card and Proton-Experimental, aswell as GE-Proton versions, so i have no suggestions to try other than what you have done.
I just tested GE-Proton-7-5 and Proton-Experimental `1646054789 experimental-7.0-20220228`

Game detects graphics settings to "Low", (after clearing the prefix 1466860) and when i set everything to max, it shows a yellow "warning" sign saying it is not optimal, but it works just fine doing that.

